?-țideț ilaq aț-țiliḍ d sebba n tuccḍa, meɛna ɣef wayen yeɛnan imukan ɣer tama-w tayeffust n Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken a k-isellek si ger ifassen-nsen. Aț-țiliḍ d sebba n uɣelluy i wid ur numin ara s Ṛebbi, s wayes ara k-d-yawi ɣer ṭṭaɛa-ines.
Daymi m'ara d-yali wasif n Urdun neɣ m'ulac a t-id-yerr ɣer webrid. Akken yura di tira iqedsen : Acḥal meqqeṛ imenɣi i deg ara d-isfehmen.
Eɛni nezmer a nḥeṛṛem seg weɣḍas deg waman wid iwumi i d-yețțunefken yiwet n tmura ? Xaṭi ! Meɛna win yeṭṭfen deg-i ur fcilen ara di lbaḍna agi, anagar wid iwumi i d-yessawel Sidi Ṛebbi ?
Tiṭ ț-țaftilt n bab n lbaṭel, acḥal daɣen yewɛeṛ : ilaq aț-țiliḍ d sebba n tuccḍa, lameɛna ma yella tesḍelm, acḥal meqqeṛ leḥmala n tideț, aț-țilim d sebba n tuccḍa.
?ef wayen yeɛnan lbaḍna n Sidna Ɛisa, i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi s lxiṛ i iṭṭef iman-is iwakken a k-id-iṭṭef si dderya-s, imi d nețța ara k-yesfehmen ayen i d-tenna ccariɛa.
Ɣef wayen yeɛnan izuṛan n lejdud-ik, ț-țamdint n Baɛwint tameqqrant ițemcabin ɣer wayeḍ. M'ara timɣuṛ-ek a tamdint i gḥekmen ɣer wemkan-ik, nețța daɣen ț-țezdeg n wul-ik alamma d ixfawen n tmurt-ik.
