A nɛeddit tura ɣer isteqsiyen i yi-d-yefka Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken a ten-isellek si snat ccetlat-agi, axaṭer aṭas n wat Isṛail. Di leɛnaya-nsen, s wakka ara yili lxilaf ger yemdanen.
