Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, ur yezdiɣ ara amkan-nni anda akken tella di lḥekma, ț-țiqeṛṛiziwin akk-d țɣuṛṛuḥin, aț-țilim d sebba n tuccḍa, ama di lawant ur nesɛi lɛib,
Deg ussan-nni, ur ilaq ara a d-yessuter i Sidi Ṛebbi i kra n wussan, ilissen azal n alaf n yergazen s wacḥal n tqecwalin i d-yegran ?
